@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1 class="text-brown text-center mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="text-dark bg-light p-4 rounded shadow-sm mx-auto" style="max-width: 800px;">
    <p>
        At <strong>EventEase</strong>, we are committed to safeguarding your personal information and maintaining your trust. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data when you interact with our venue booking platform.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-4 h5 text-brown">1. Data We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3">
        <li class="list-group-item">Contact Information: Includes your full name, email address, and phone number.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Booking Information: Details of your event bookings, selected venues, and schedules.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Technical Information: Browser type, device identifiers, location data, and site usage.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4 h5 text-brown">2. Purpose of Data Collection</h2>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3">
        <li class="list-group-item">To facilitate bookings and provide efficient customer service.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">To customize your experience based on preferences and behavior.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">To ensure platform security and analyze performance trends.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4 h5 text-brown">3. Sharing of Information</h2>
    <p>
        We only share your information with trusted third-party providers who help us deliver our services—such as payment processors and cloud hosting partners. We never sell your data.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-4 h5 text-brown">4. Your Data Protection</h2>
    <p>
        Your privacy is protected through robust encryption, access controls, and regular system audits. We ensure your personal information is stored securely and only accessed when necessary.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-4 h5 text-brown">5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
    <p>
        You can request to access, update, or delete your personal data at any time. To exercise your rights, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@eventease.com">support@eventease.com</a>.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4">
        This policy may be revised from time to time. By continuing to use EventEase, you agree to the terms outlined in the most recent version of our Privacy Policy.
    </p>
</div>

<style>
    .text-brown {
        color: #8B4513;
    }
</style>
